---
title: Sesame Chicken Rice Bowl with aubergine and bell peppers
description: Sesame coated chicken is baked to crispy perfection in this Asian-inspired recipe. To make things even more aromatic the base of the bowl—aubergine and bell pepper—are cooked together with ginger and garlic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R01_W17_IE_IEXCFC0144-2_Main__3high-986d62f1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/sesame-chicken-rice-bowl-63d8df50db1fd0bc84bb96f5-6f811969.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/sesame-chicken-rice-bowl-63d8df50db1fd0bc84bb96f5
author: HelloFresh
